title: SnowEx17 P-3 Airborne Video V001
summary: This data set contains video footage of two locations in Colorado, USA: Grand Mesa, a snow-covered forested study site about 40 miles east of Grand Junction, and Senator Beck Basin, approximately 80 miles to the SSE of Grand Mesa. Video footage was captured using a video camera mounted to the belly of a P-3 aircraft during the 2017 SnowEx science flights. The video footage is raw.
